metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Frogs is more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension and Chord Progression Novelty.
key_conclusion: Frogs has sections analyzed in the following keys: E♭ Dorian, G♭ Lydian,  and B Minor.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!
